  "title": "Management Associates (Central | $3000 to $5000 | Training Provided)",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>MNC </strong></li><li><strong>Working Location: Central, Singapore </strong></li><li><strong>Basic: $3000 to $5000 + Commission </strong></li><li><strong>Flexible Working Hours</strong></li><li><strong>Good communication & people's skills</strong></li><li><strong>Training Provided</strong></li></ul><p><strong></strong></p><p>Job Responsibilities: <br /></p><ul><li>Support senior consultants during client meetings, reviews, and follow-ups</li><li>Prepare client documentation, proposals, and presentation materials</li><li>Develop strong communication, presentation, and relationship-management skills</li><li>Participate in structured training, mentoring, and professional development programmes</li><li>Build professional networks and long-term client relationships over time</li><li>Ensure all activities comply with company and regulatory guidelines</li><li>Advise and recommend suitable products for clients.</li></ul><p></p><p>Requirements:<br /></p><ul><li>GCE A level / Diploma and/or Degree in related field </li><li>Candidate without experience are welcome to apply – Training will be provided</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now button</strong> with the following information\nin the resume</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>NG DIAUM YEE (R2198031)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
